<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>At Sisyphus Chat, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our services.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect minimal information necessary to provide you with a secure and private communication experience. The types of data we may collect include:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Your username, email address, and phone number for account creation and authentication purposes.</li>
    <li><strong>Message Data:</strong> All messages are end-to-end encrypted. We cannot access the content of your messages, and no unencrypted data is stored on our servers.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Non-identifiable device metadata such as operating system version and app version for performance improvements and bug fixes.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the information we collect in the following ways:</p>
<ul>
    <li>To create and manage your account on Sisyphus Chat.</li>
    <li>To maintain the security and functionality of our service.</li>
    <li>To provide customer support and address any technical issues.</li>
    <li>To analyze anonymized data for performance optimization.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
<p>Your data is not shared with third parties, advertisers, or external services. We do not sell or rent your personal information. The only exception to this rule is if we are required to comply with a lawful request from a government agency or law enforcement, in which case, due process will be followed, and you will be notified, if permissible by law.</p>

<h2>4. Data Security</h2>
<p>We employ advanced security measures, including encryption technologies, to safeguard your data from unauthorized access. All communication through Sisyphus Chat is encrypted from start to finish, ensuring that only the intended recipient can read your messages.</p>

<h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
<p>As a user of Sisyphus Chat, you have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Access your personal information.</li>
    <li>Request corrections to any inaccurate information.</li>
    <li>Delete your account and associated data at any time.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
<p>Sisyphus Chat does not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics services. Your privacy is paramount, and we aim to maintain a zero-tracking approach wherever possible.</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. When changes are made, we will notify you via email or in-app notifications. The date of the latest revision will be clearly marked at the top of this page.</p>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, feel free to reach out to us.</p>